A grimy dwarf weed is the second-highest level herb. A player with 70 Herblore may clean it and produce a dwarf weed for 13.8 Herblore experience. Dwarf weed is mainly used to create ranging potions.

It may be grown from a dwarf weed seed at 79 Farming, granting 192 experience per herb during harvest.

Changes[edit | edit source]

Date Changes
12 August 2020
(update)

Composting grimy dwarf weed will now yield supercompost instead of regular compost.

9 March 2017
(update)

The item's value was increased from 1 to 24.

26 February 2015
(update)
  • The item was graphically updated to distinguish it from other grimy herbs.
  • The item was renamed from "Herb" to "Grimy dwarf weed".
  • The item was made tradeable on the Trading Post/Grand Exchange.
  • The “Identify” option was changed to a “Clean” option.
25 February 2013
(update)
  • The item was renamed from "Grimy dwarf weed" to "Herb".
  • The "Clean" option was changed to an "Identify" option.
22 February 2013
(update)
  • The item was renamed from "Herb" to "Grimy dwarf weed".
  • The "Identify" option was changed to a "Clean" option.
